    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      55.79,
      526.42,
      96.69
    ],
    "text": "Acting on a tip-off, officers attached to the Walana Central Anti-Corruption Unit conducted a raid in the Borupana area of the Mount Lavinia Police Division on the evening of 17 July 2026.",
    "fonts": [
