      107.17,
      526.4,
      148.05
    ],
    "text": "During the operation, a suspect was arrested in possession of 75 litres (100 bottles) of illicit liquor. The suspect and the seized liquor were handed over to the Mount Lavinia Police Station for further legal action.",
