      644.85,
      526.41,
      685.61
    ],
    "text": "A team of officers from the Dankotuwa Police Station, acting on a tip-off, conducted a raid in the Katukenda area of the Dankotuwa Police Division on the night of 17 July 2026.",
    "fonts": [
