      418.74,
      526.38,
      459.62
    ],
    "text": "Acting on intelligence received, officers from the Bagawanthalawa Police Station conducted a raid at the Keselgamuwa Reserve in the Oldi area of the Bagawanthalawa Police Division on the afternoon of 17 July 2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
