    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      470.1,
      526.29,
      510.98
    ],
    "text": "During the operation, three suspects were arrested for allegedly engaging in unauthorised gem mining without valid permits. Police also seized equipment believed to have been used in the illegal mining activities.",
